Rating: 2
I found this dish to be edible, but very bland. It could definately use some lemon, salt and pepper, garlic and maybe herbs. You could barely taste the jalapeno. No one was impressed, and either picked at the clams, veggies or sauce seperately.

Rating: 4
This was my first attempt at cooking clams, and this was a cinch. The flavors were so good, and I mopped up all of the juices with some bread. v.g.